      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Watch carefully. \n\nA pattern of tiles will light up on the board. Each
    tile will glow one at a time in a specific order. \n\nThe sequence will play
    twice. Pay attention, the order matters. \n\nWhen the lights disappear, it\u2019s
    your turn. \n\nClick the tiles in the exact same order you saw them. \n\nIf you
    choose the correct sequence, you\u2019ll unlock a hidden clue. \n\nIf you make
    a mistake, the pattern will reset and play again. Take your time. Focus. \n\nReady?
    \n\nPress Start when you\u2019re prepared to test your memory. \n\n "
